# Workers static assets redirects (same syntax as the old Pages _redirects).
#
# The site builds with base=/transformers/ (its mount path on the family hub
# domain), but Astro emits files at the dist root. So: send the bare root to the
# canonical base path, normalize the slashless base path, and rewrite (200, no
# redirect) base-prefixed URLs onto the real asset paths at the dist root.
# (Mirrors guides-ai-engineering/public/_redirects; scaffold nav links are
# base-aware as of book-scaffold-astro v4.24.0, #140/#141.)
/ /transformers/ 302
/transformers /transformers/ 302
/transformers/* /:splat 200
